  • Classes in edu.ncsu.csc216.get_outdoors.model used by edu.ncsu.csc216.get_outdoors 
    Class and Description
    ActivityList
    ActivityList is both OBSERVABLE by GetOutdoorsManager and an OBSERVER of Activity.
    Park
    A Park in the GetOutdoors system represents a collection of trails for a single park in the system.
    ParkList
    A container object for Park objects.
    TrailList
    A TrailList maintains a collection of Trails in the system, providing functionality adding and removing trails, notifying Trails when a Park's snowChange field is updated, and returning display arrays for the Trails in a Park.
  • Classes in edu.ncsu.csc216.get_outdoors.model used by edu.ncsu.csc216.get_outdoors.model 
    Class and Description
    Activity
    An object representing an Activity that can be performed on a Trail in a Park.
    Park
    A Park in the GetOutdoors system represents a collection of trails for a single park in the system.
    Tabular
    Classes that implement this interface provide a method for extracting a list of elements as a 2-dimensional array, where each element of the list is represented as a "row" and each field in an element is a "column" in the 2D array.
    Trail
    An object representing a Trail contained by a Park.
